Refactored leaderboard utility, leaderboard activity.
Started transitioning gamemanager's canvas based logic to canvas utility.
Fixed bug
End of game redirects users to leaderboard.

Moved GameManager's draw method over into CanvasUtility.
Refactored GameManager's static variables.

Updated player mana updates to the server's sent updates.
Changed the alpha and location on displayed chat messages.
Updated loading screen utility test.
Updated tests and offloaded some more of GameManager's work to Player.
"Play again" button (on leaderboard page) does not appear until a game has been played.
